headline: Match Group to Announce Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2025 Results
summary: Match Group (NASDAQ: MTCH) will release financial results for the fourth quarter and full year 2025 on Tuesday, February 3, 2026 after-market close. The company will host its quarterly conference call to discuss these results at 5:00 p.m. ET on the same day.
